lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"所以我哋就要監察泛民政客<br />\n因為我哋以立會過半為目的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"監察？<br />\n<br />\n無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每屆只能投或不投<br />\n<br />\n投完做到，只能睇下屆仲要唔要投<br />\n<br />\n呢刻個目標係針對35+，做到35+，班友做唔到35+後應該嘅後果，下屆無人投佢哋，呢啲先係選舉吧？"},{"pid":"be82e90a5e8b197aea1cfbfa683aa4240abcbda8","tid":1933231,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"有初選當然好，不過都有好多問題要解決。<br />\n<br />\n１）選舉開支。<br />\n２）對素人本土不利（知名度越高越有利）<br />\n３）要點樣既初選？得罪講句，如果張超雄下屆決定再玩，而佢又贏初選，大家係咪又乖乖配票俾佢？<br />\n<br />\n理論上有初選當然最好，但民主派黨性不如少數奶共派，如果九龍東都傾唔掂數，其他區更難攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4684c6f0bf21d623ab7a2ce7f3a72dd87ffe10","tid":1933231,"uid":34424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"你話本土派輸打贏要都好 本土只會投比本土 無可否認好多選民只係見邊個出名就投邊個 <br />\n<br />\n資源多之下 最後都係投晒比泛民 最後呢四年一次嘅所謂選舉 最後都係跟返泛民同建制嘅遊戲規則玩 屆屆叫人含淚投泛民<br />\n<br />\n而泛民就算做得幾差 做幾多出賣香港人嘅嘢都好 都冇人會理"},{"pid":"4a5f296ea640f0398a1359d1fec66e6a4e31f168","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be82e90a5e8b197aea1cfbfa683aa4240abcbda8","tid":1933231,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"有初選當然好，不過都有好多問題要解決。<br />\n<br />\n１）選舉開支。<br />\n２）對素人本土不利（知名度越高越有利）<br />\n３）要點樣既初選？得罪講句，如果張超雄下屆決定再玩，而佢又贏初選，大家係咪又乖乖配票俾佢？<br />\n<br />\n理論上有初選當然最好，但民主派黨性不如少數奶共派，如果九龍東都傾唔掂數，其他區更難攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:27:59.000Z","msg":"素人問題就係有人做左區議員就幻想自己可以做埋立法會議員<br />\n<br />\n戴耀庭有個計劃係可以解決選舉開支嘅問題"},{"pid":"4bf208ee0a2455ed94e55ca062edcdc3382ea608","tid":1933231,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b66ad0b9540f24315483a8816488c8bd98ed7fd","tid":1933231,"uid":45708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b1348cc2fc8fc0b5fdd5bfb4eb4ebd5ec5713674","tid":1933231,"uid":16086,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"泛民：搞初選姐係自己輸冇得出人，所以直頭唔搞<br />\n我真係dllm，比熱狗白兵嗰啲屌，我地都幫你地護航<br />\n一句講曬，冇初選我連本土都唔撚會投，<br />\n屌你老母咁鍾意攬炒，就同你攬炒<br />\n你老母嬲撚到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"而家係初選對素人同本土派不利啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"素人 要參加 冇人阻到<br />\n<br />\n但 泛民初選 關本土 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55580a0a9772eb771a1db92bfb0a237bda2c6add","tid":1933231,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac138294cb6ee55a3ec9c50634f04ac5e60f2115","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf208ee0a2455ed94e55ca062edcdc3382ea608","tid":1933231,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b66ad0b9540f24315483a8816488c8bd98ed7fd","tid":1933231,"uid":45708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b1348cc2fc8fc0b5fdd5bfb4eb4ebd5ec5713674","tid":1933231,"uid":16086,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"泛民：搞初選姐係自己輸冇得出人，所以直頭唔搞<br />\n我真係dllm，比熱狗白兵嗰啲屌，我地都幫你地護航<br />\n一句講曬，冇初選我連本土都唔撚會投，<br />\n屌你老母咁鍾意攬炒，就同你攬炒<br />\n你老母嬲撚到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"而家係初選對素人同本土派不利啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"素人 要參加 冇人阻到<br />\n<br />\n但 泛民初選 關本土 咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"泛民初選就係增加民主陣營立會議席<br />\n當然包括本土"},{"pid":"b2160ec2324e3f5a7dba7b748b4a8d8fe1aba573","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:45:09.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n泛民睇唔睇到呀？"},{"pid":"0ba7c6faa1cebde8e55a60c373b71ab9a7c588fb","tid":1933231,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"652da42bd89ede4e6311149e8b70a041a7570759","tid":1933231,"uid":45708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ce79a28db8e6460ab9234833b14ee76d41f6046","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5b66ad0b9540f24315483a8816488c8bd98ed7fd","tid":1933231,"uid":45708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"而家係初選對素人同本土派不利啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:36:54.000Z","msg":"邊講話一定不利？<br />\n如果出嚟互𠝹票， 就梗係不利"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"選管會規定初選計選舉開支，如果照搞初選好大機會傳統泛民贏哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"已經同你係另一個post解釋過初選計選舉開支係對泛民不利，對素人有利。真唔明定假唔明？"},{"pid":"1500647c7e7a437eb7d9d9a4364e8658868a7685","tid":1933231,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8d1bc0dc37b61f5cb4047987925c9e88400626","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n一定要初選<br />\n唔含呀"},{"pid":"d36f86880476a72a1cefad1da85536a2a7c11b9b","tid":1933231,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04e97af7122b6ab197f16cb57cdad7c89fd549d7","tid":1933231,"uid":254551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"初選有無都算<br />\n唔好搶票得唔得<br />\n合作搞一次大野丫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"如果立法會選舉真係想協調得到嘅話，唔係無辦法，就係學中聯辦嘅做法--------配票 ! <br />\n<br />\n從區議會選舉，可以獲得準確的票數分佈資訊，從而為立法會選票配票所用。區選與立選相隔不足一年，而且個數據精細到選區level。區議員日常同街坊接觸，比起透過網上平台配票，更有信服力。數據又係現成嘅，又唔使怕五毛搞搞震、俾人hack之類。<br />\n<br />\n按此，可以推算出每個票站嘅嘅黃色選民比例，用區議會選區為單位配票：每個黃色區議員，喺自己所屬果一區，宣傳按機制所推舉嘅民主派立法會候選人。<br />\n<br />\n當然，有部分選民係唔會跟足配票，但可以喺計算時計入allowance與走盞位。"},{"pid":"be364ee4e4d77765f2ebb74cd8d56f74db53007b","tid":1933231,"uid":21817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T10:59:59.000Z","msg":"如果素人/本土自己唔願意參加初選咁點？<br />\n傳統泛民自己選自己？"},{"pid":"1bb4c1c79c88d541a553a5367a2edaa331a61058","tid":1933231,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"依家似係素人同本土唔肯初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你個初選得泛民都冇用啦<br />\n支持初選"},{"pid":"7a27af6355e96cf4a6aa4ccbde5167ffccc31ba0","tid":1933231,"uid":103235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"睇下新聞啦，本土同素人唔想初選呀"},{"pid":"3018fe34f3e4e311184a08e5dea7d532952664b2","tid":1933231,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"又標題撚<br />\n人地九龍東第一次開會未有最終協調<br />\n就講到泛民話唔搞初選"},{"pid":"7562997a8003d8d6136a829a13a6ed2a13dc5b71","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3018fe34f3e4e311184a08e5dea7d532952664b2","tid":1933231,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"又標題撚<br />\n人地九龍東第一次開會未有最終協調<br />\n就講到泛民話唔搞初選"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"有三個黨唔想初選呀<br />\n你問下有分開會個d 人呀"},{"pid":"0dcec7f243e05ef66ce90eef57d83ea018f49792","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a27af6355e96cf4a6aa4ccbde5167ffccc31ba0","tid":1933231,"uid":103235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"睇下新聞啦，本土同素人唔想初選呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"有三個黨唔想初選呀<br />\n你問下有份開九東會個d 人呀"},{"pid":"b2c322cb39f46f0b0bbd4e8561c506385490af5b","tid":1933231,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1348cc2fc8fc0b5fdd5bfb4eb4ebd5ec5713674","tid":1933231,"uid":16086,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"泛民：搞初選姐係自己輸冇得出人，所以直頭唔搞<br />\n我真係dllm，比熱狗白兵嗰啲屌，我地都幫你地護航<br />\n一句講曬，冇初選我連本土都唔撚會投，<br />\n屌你老母咁鍾意攬炒，就同你攬炒<br />\n你老母嬲撚到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"正，有初選都攬炒先啱"},{"pid":"289637e5532a450d69a0fbddadbe502297a06298","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf8fccbeb2aee383ab68826d1f67186ea3a86384","tid":1933231,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"good night sir"},{"pid":"53d05f35f5f115d4eafb7c4c5ebdc39d1049f9c8","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf8fccbeb2aee383ab68826d1f67186ea3a86384","tid":1933231,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"good night sir"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T18:46:05.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n狗識政治就唔駛做狗啦"},{"pid":"96dbad23963c6873c95d202813246ad480fbb8a4","tid":1933231,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T01:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40101661442a7589b0e20cd17be765176cf008f","tid":1933231,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59124508f481b5256c4e1953129553cdc8e6f5f5","tid":1933231,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb96c1a1cc19127259736d64cb1fd5863752cf17","tid":1933231,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"沈博士提出進攻功能組別<br />\n作為一般選民/香港人，我哋面對白票黨/熱狗/白兵等攻擊/ 冷嘲熱諷， 都為今年立法會選舉爭取個半議席補駕護航，我哋支持民主陣營有初選機制就係為咗爭取立法會最多議席<br />\n果然泛民主派一句沒有初選就推到我哋所有心血<br />\n如果泛民主派唔想贏，我哋都冇需要幫佢保住份工<br />\n沒有初選，一係投本土，一係投白票<br />\n唔會再含淚<br />\n<br />\n幫手推推<br />\n民間自救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"投白票就係支那狗."}]}